 <name>Stagehand_FSM</name>
 <channel>pear.hatotech.org</channel>
 <summary>A Finite State Machine.</summary>
 <description>Stagehand_FSM provides a self configuring Finite State Machine(FSM).
The following is a list of features of Stagehand_FSM.
o Transition action
o Entry and Exit state actions
o Initial and Final pseudo states
o Nested FSM
o History Marker
o Activity
o User defined payload</description>
